Ablo new, existin an deletit owersettin units is leetit

pt-movepage-action-check: Check gif the muiv is possible
pt-movepage-intro:
This byordinair page permits ye tae muiv pages that ar maurkt fer owersetin.
The muiv action will na be instant, cause monie pages will need tae be muived.
While the pages ar bein muived, it's na possible tae interact wi the said pages.
Failures will be loggit in the [[Special:Log/pagetranslation|page owersetin log]] n thay need tae be repaired bi haun.
pt-movepage-started:
The base page haes nou been muived.
Please check the [[Special:Log/pagetranslation|page owersetin log]] fer mistaks n compleation message.
pt-locked-page: This page is lockt cause the owersetable page is nou bein muived.
pt-deletepage-invalid-text: The speceefied page isna aen owersetable page or aen owersetin page.
pt-deletepage-action-check: Leet the pages tae be deletit
pt-deletepage-any-legend: Delete owersettable page, message bundle or owersettin page
pt-deletepage-started: Please check the [[Special:Log/pagetranslation|page owersetin log]] fer mistaks n compleation message.
pt-deletepage-intro:
This byordinair page permits ye tae delete ae hale owersettable page, or ae individual owersettin page in ae leid.
The delete action willna be instant, acause aw the pages dependin on thaim will be deletit an aa.
Failures will be loggit in the [[Special:Log/pagetranslation|page owersettin log]] an thay need tae be mendit bi haund.
